      <txt c="X" a="X" r="X" s="2" w="850" x="40" y="80" delay="0" pt="1" e="-3" align="left">A customs official demanded a payment from the Captain. However, together with the agent, they managed to avoid paying.

What should they do now?</txt>
      <txt c="X" s="2" y="190" delay="0" crct="30" align="left">No payment was made so there is nothing to report</txt>
      <txt c="X" s="2" y="260" delay="0" crct="44" align="left">Report the demand in order to share best practices</txt>
